Indirect recursive call via application callback: MHD_add_connection -> internal_add_connection -> new_connection_prepare_ -> daemon->apc(...) (application-provided acceptance policy callback) -> application callback calls MHD_add_connection (directly or via another path). This produces an indirect recursion (MHD_add_connection calling itself), violating MISRA C 2023 Rule 17.2.
